Evraz to Pay $402 Million Special Dividend, $89 Million Interim

-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 
2011-10-12T06:13:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/evraz-to-pay-402-million-special-dividend-89-million-interim.html
Evraz Group SA (EVR)  will pay a special
dividend of $402 million as well as an interim dividend of $89
million, the Russian steel and coal producer said today in a
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Khrennikov in Moscow at 
 ikhrennikov@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
